    <item>
      <title>拜耳因利润预期减弱而跌至二十年来最低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/bayer-lower-earnings-guidance-on-weak-crop-unit-performance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国企业集团拜耳下调了今年的利润预期并表示 2025 年盈利可能下降，此后该公司股价跌至 20 年来最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/bayer-lower-earnings-guidance-on-weak-crop-unit-performance</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 06:53:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
